界面新闻是中国具有影响力的原创财经新媒体，只服务于独立思考的人群。
Interface News is an original and influential new financial media in China, serving only the people who think independently.
记者：余瑾毅、通讯员薛源 本文来源：湖北日报“ 因新冠肺炎导致呼吸衰竭，在“鬼门关”走了一遭的1岁男童牛牛（化名），经武汉儿童医院重症医学科全力救治保住性命，2月13日，家人将已确认符合出院标准的他接回家继续隔离观察。
Journalist: Yu Jinyi, Correspondent Xue Yuan: Hubei Daily, 1-year-old boy cattle and cattle (alias) who had been dying from respiratory failure caused by Xinguan pneumonia saved his life after intensive medical treatment in Wuhan Children's Hospital on February 13.
”因新冠肺炎导致呼吸衰竭，在“鬼门关”走了一遭的1岁男童牛牛（化名），经武汉儿童医院重症医学科全力救治保住性命，2月13日，家人将已确认符合出院标准的他接回家继续隔离观察。
A 1-year-old boy, a cow and cow (alias) who had been taken to the "ghost gate" after suffering respiratory failure as a result of pneumonia, survived intensive medical treatment at Wuhan Children's Hospital on February 13.
牛牛准备出院了1月26日下午，家住武汉市黄陂区的牛牛，因间断腹泻、呕吐6天，发热，精神萎靡，食欲欠佳，尿量少，出现呼吸急促，被送入武汉儿童医院急诊科救治，紧急收入该院重症医学科隔离病房救治。
On the afternoon of January 26, cows and cows of Huangpi District, Wuhan, were sent to Wuhan Children's Hospital Emergency Department for emergency treatment because of intermittent diarrhea, vomiting for six days, fever, mental malaise, poor appetite, low urine output and shortness of breath.
Play省市联合医疗专家组成员、武汉儿童医院重症医学科主任医师张芙蓉带领团队，立即研判病情，展开抢救。
Play provincial and municipal joint medical expert group members, Wuhan Children's Hospital severe medicine chief physician Zhang Furong led the team, immediately investigate the disease, launched rescue.
入科时患儿经皮氧饱和度仅仅只有80%，在予以气管插管，呼吸机辅助通气后，患儿的氧饱和度仍不能维持正常，随时面临呼吸衰竭，有生命危险。
The percutaneous oxygen saturation of children is only 80%. After trachea intubation and ventilator-assisted ventilation, the oxygen saturation of the children is still not normal and they are exposed to respiratory failure at any time, which is life threatening.
医护们为他的病情捏了一把汗。
The doctors pinched his illness.
胸部CT提示，牛牛双肺感染，高度疑似新型冠状病毒肺炎，肾功能出现异常。
Chest CT findings, cattle and cattle lung infection, a high level of suspected new coronavirus pneumonia, abnormal renal function.
重症医学科医疗组精心诊治，为牛牛行连续血液净化、持续给予抗病毒、抗感染等治疗，并使用丙种球蛋白提高免疫力、营养支持、维持内环境稳定等综合治疗，稳定住牛牛的病情。
The intensive medical team provides intensive care for continuous blood purification, continuous antiviral and anti-infection treatment for cattle and cattle, and uses gamma globulin to enhance immunity, nutritional support and maintain internal environmental stability.
牛牛在接受治疗经过治疗，牛牛的状况一天天好起来。
Cattle and cattle are being treated and their condition is getting better day by day.
2月6日，牛牛成功脱离呼吸机并拔除气管插管。
On 6 February, cattle were successfully removed from the ventilator and the trachea intubation was removed.
生命体征逐渐稳定，肺部感染已基本吸收。
The vital signs are gradually stable and the pulmonary infection has been largely absorbed.
在两次核酸检测确认为阴性后，医务人员判定他已达到出院标准。
After two negative nucleic acid tests, medical staff determined that he met the discharge criteria.
张芙蓉主任介绍，牛牛新型冠状病毒核酸检测呈阳性，影像学符合肺炎表现，同时伴有休克、急性呼吸窘迫综合征、急性肾衰竭，依据“新型冠状病毒感染的肺炎诊疗方案（试行第五版）”和“湖北省儿童新型冠状病毒（2019-nCoV）感染诊疗建议”，被诊断为危重型新型冠状病毒肺炎，是国内首例确诊的危重型新型冠状病毒肺炎儿童患者。
The new coronavirus nucleic acid test in cattle and cattle is positive, and the imaging studies are consistent with pneumonia, accompanied by shock, acute respiratory distress syndrome and acute renal failure, "Zhang said.
“新型冠状肺炎是以发热、咳嗽为主要表现，但该患儿是以消化道症状起病，主要表现为呕吐、腹泻，起病早期呼吸道症状不明显，之后快速进展为急性呼吸窘迫综合征、脓毒症休克并伴有急性肾衰竭。
"The new type of coronary pneumonia is characterized by fever and cough, but the main symptoms of the child's digestive tract are vomiting, diarrhea, early respiratory symptoms are not obvious, then rapid progress to acute respiratory distress syndrome, sepsis shock with acute renal failure.
”张芙蓉主任提示，专家、医务人员需重视部分无明显呼吸道症状的儿童病例。
Zhang suggested that experts and medical staff should pay attention to some cases of children without obvious respiratory symptoms.
张芙蓉主任介绍，家庭聚集性发病是儿童新冠病毒肺炎疫情的重要流行特征，家庭内密切接触是儿童新型冠状病毒感染的主要方式。
Director Zhang Furong said that family gathering was an important epidemic characteristic of the children's new coronavirus pneumonia. Close contact within the family is the main way to infect children with the new coronavirus.
牛牛属于非家庭聚集病例，家人至今未出现新冠肺炎典型症状，但其父母未进行新型冠状病毒核酸检测，不能排除是无症状感染者。
Niu cattle is a non-family case, the family members have not yet presented with typical symptoms of coronavirus, but their parents did not have a new coronavirus nucleic acid test, can not be ruled out asymptomatic infection.
“从目前的诊疗经验来看，大部分新冠病毒感染儿童患者属普通型，危重型新冠病毒肺炎儿童患者不多。
"Based on current clinical experience, the majority of children with new crown virus infection are of the normal type, and the number of children with critical new crown virus pneumonia is not high."
”张芙蓉主任强调，家长们不必太过恐慌，但也不能掉以轻心。
"Zhang stressed that parents should not panic too much, but they should not take it lightly.
如果孩子密切接触过新型冠状病毒感染的肺炎确诊病例，应对孩子密切关注。
If the child has been in close contact with the newly confirmed case of coronavirus infection pneumonia, the child should be closely monitored.
一旦孩子出现呼吸道症状，应立即就诊。
If the child develops respiratory symptoms, he should see a doctor immediately.
如果孩子没有相关接触史，出现轻微的咳嗽、流涕等呼吸道症状，体温不超过38.5℃，能吃能睡能玩，可以先居家隔离观察、对症处理；如果孩子精神萎靡，食欲下降，呼吸不畅，高热不退，咳嗽明显，特别是小于6个月的婴儿，应及时就诊。
If the child does not have relevant contact history, there is mild cough, runny nose and other respiratory symptoms, body temperature does not exceed 38.5 degrees Celsius, can eat can sleep can play, can be isolated first observation, symptomatic treatment; if the child is depressed, appetite reduced, breathing poor, high fever, cough obvious, especially less than 6 months old, should see a doctor promptly.
